1 (i) Create and abolish any position other than one specifically
2 provided for in this title; and
3 (ii) Determine the qualification, appointment, removal, term, and
4 tenure of its employees.
5 (2) The Administration may determine the compensation of:
6 (i) Employees if the compensation is determined pursuant to
7 Subtitle 6 of this title;
8 (ii) Executive management positions, as recommended by the
